[[module CSS]]
.heritage-notice {
border: dashed 2px #b00010;
border-radius: 10px;
width: 400px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 0 20px;
background: #fcfcf0 url(/local--files/heritage-collection/hatch-black10i.png);
color: #331010;
min-height: 116px;
}

table.heritage {
  border: 0;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 auto;
  width: 600px;
  border-spacing: 0;
  border-collapse: separate;
}

table.heritage td {
  vertical-align: top;
}

table.heritage td.title,
table.heritage td.label {
  border-right: solid 1px #999;
  font-size: 16pt;
  color: #999;
  width: 200px;
  text-align: right;
  padding-right: 10px;
}

table.heritage td.label {
  font-size: 20pt;
}

table.heritage td.title {
  padding-bottom: 20px;
}
table.heritage td.label {
  font-weight: bold;
}

table.heritage td.entry {
  padding: 6px 0 20px 10px;
}

table.heritage div.description {
  font-size: 14pt;
}
table.heritage div.snippet {
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 8pt;
  color: #666;
}
table.heritage div.date {
  font-weight: normal;
  font-size: 7pt;
}
table.heritage div.snippet p {
  margin: 5px 0;
}
table.heritage div.description p,
table.heritage div.date p {
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 599px) {
.heritage-notice {
padding: 0;
}

table.heritage {
width: 100%;
}

table.heritage td.title, table.heritage td.label {
width: 40%;
}

table.heritage td.label {
font-size: 15pt;
}
}
[[/module]]

[[table class="heritage" cellspacing="0"]]
[[row]]
[[cell class="title"]]
稿件公示
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]

[[row]]
[[cell class="label"]]
[[[SCP-CN-1091]]]
[[div class="date"]]
“不要唤醒湖底的黑王。”

[[/div]]
[[/cell]]
[[cell class="entry"]]
[[div style="background-color: transparent; padding-left: 7px;border-left: solid 10px #5e5e5e; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;"]]
[[div class="description"]]
草稿提供者：[[*user W Asriel]]
改稿者：[[*user Enflowerz]]
2019年12月精品条目
[[/div]]
[[div class="snippet"]]
“战争之恶、黑王之恶，如此清晰地呈现于读者眼前……让来自异世界的压抑与紧迫感隐隐浮现。”——[[*user W Asriel]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]

[[row]]
[[cell class="label"]]
[[[grant-request-for-surgery-strengthens-the-body|批准通過手術強化人體奇術構造以達到高效驅散非物質實體之目的的申請]]]
[[div class="date"]]
“若我們研發出一能配戴此一靜態物品的活動項目，甚至此活動項目也有能力進行驅魔、消滅惡魔類實體呢，則無疑更能夠保護客戶的安全。”

[[/div]]
[[/cell]]
[[cell class="entry"]]
[[div style="background-color: transparent; padding-left: 7px;border-left: solid 10px #5e5e5e; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;"]]
[[div class="description"]]
草稿提供者：[[*user DF-thirteen]]
改稿者：[[*user Reverberate_a]]
2021年12月精品条目
[[/div]]
[[div class="snippet"]]
“点子能被残响老师接到而且写得这——（比划）么棒实在是感到万分荣幸……真的写得非常专业，能看到此等佳作还奢求什么期限呢。”——[[*user DF-thirteen]]
“有機會寫到以往沒有接觸過的GOI格式也很開心。”——[[*user Reverberate_a]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]


[[/table]]

[[module CSS]]
#header {
    height: 140px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    padding-bottom: 22px; /* FOR MENU */
    background: none;
    opacity: 0.8;
}

#header{
    background: url(null)
}
#header:before{
display:block;
position: absolute;
width: 100px;
height: 100px;
top: 22%;
left:2%;
z-index: -1;
content: "";
background:url(http://scpsandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/collab%3Adraft-swap-hub/ogspin);
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-size:100px 100px;
background-position: 0px 0px;
z-index: 201;
  animation: spinny1 9s ease infinite;
}

/*
CC BY-SA 3.0
spinny
ikr_4185
 */
@keyframes spinny1 {
    0% {
      -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1);
    }
    100% {
      -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1);
      transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1);
    }
}


#header:after{
display:block;
position: absolute;
width: 100px;
height: 100px;
top: 22%;
left:2%;
z-index: -2;
content: "";
background:url(http://topia.wdfiles.com/local--files/niconews/spin2.png);
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-size:100px 100px;
background-position: 0px 0px;
z-index: 200;
}

/*
CC BY-SA 3.0
spinny
ikr_4185
 */
@keyframes spinny2 {
    0% {
      -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      -webkit-transform: rotate(60deg) scale(1);
      transform: rotate(60deg) scale(1);

    }
    100% {
      -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1);
      transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1);
    }
}
#header h1 a::before {
    content: "你的鸽子，我来炖";
    color: white;
}
#header h1 a span{
    display: block;
    content: "";
    visibility: hidden;
}
#header h2 span {
    display: block;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 19px 0;
    line-height: 0px;
    max-height: 0px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: none;
}
#header h2 span::before {
    content: "你领到了哪一只？";
    display: block;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0px 0;
    line-height: 0px;
    max-height: 0px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.8);

#side-bar .side-block {
    padding: 10px;
    border: 3px double #9c3111;
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(102,0,0,.5);
    background: #fff;
}
[[/module]]
